int MEConnectionInfoBox::getTurnDescription (   ) 
 

Get the integer value for the turndescription that is displayed in the box.

The reason for using an int is to be able to return error (a negative value).

Parameters:
If positive (or zero), the integer value of the enumeration that is printed in this box. If negative, no valid turn-direction in the box.
